Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.85,0:00:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.85,0:00:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翌晨的陽光就快來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.92,0:00:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照進這間充滿煙蒂\N雜亂無章的屋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.86,0:00:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why 聖母瑪利亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.90,0:00:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對溫柔感到飢渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.11,0:00:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.91,0:00:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼孤單的夜晚\N總是如此漫長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.75,0:00:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛仔褲下的膝蓋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.62,0:00:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被破碎的夢想打溼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.96,0:01:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著襯衫的胸部太過耀眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.00,0:01:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.89,0:01:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師,起床了,起床了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.33,0:01:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師快點起床啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.67,0:01:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點,味噌湯會涼掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.30,0:01:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦,好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.04,0:01:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是不會照顧自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.98,0:01:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種狀況\N要持續到什麼時候呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.09,0:01:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.82,0:02:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊什麼啊\N就是五代跟那個女孩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.86,0:02:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.99,0:02:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還裝糊塗,妳明明最在意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.26,0:02:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.77,0:02:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔,掃墓的日子又到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.01,0:02:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#76 我會等你的!\N響子突然的含意深深宣言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.25,0:02:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,那個高中女生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.09,0:02:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代還真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.32,0:02:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有資格說他嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.19,0:02:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說你要跟相親的對象\N一刀兩斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.33,0:02:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果現在怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.63,0:02:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還糾纏不清不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.74,0:02:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.74,0:02:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹教練,有你的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.08,0:02:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.28,0:03:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼,這些男人都一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.82,0:03:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是叔叔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.46,0:03:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?今天?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.83,0:03:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.76,0:03:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之瀨太太,妳好討厭喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候她老公的表情\N真的很好笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.50,0:03:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這樣笑人家啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.60,0:03:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是真的很好笑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.38,0:03:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能老是跟那個狗小姐\N糾纏不清
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.82,0:03:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何\N今天一定要明白的拒絕她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.87,0:04:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底有什麼事啊,突然把我叫出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.07,0:04:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要談下聘日子的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.61,0:04:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下聘?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.61,0:04:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高不高興?你很高興吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.72,0:04:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了?阿瞬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.69,0:04:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜小姐已經等很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.83,0:04:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.13,0:04:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.27,0:04:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎,歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.77,0:04:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.51,0:04:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這小子,竟然害羞起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.48,0:04:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.44,0:04:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是這樣\N細節讓我們來談就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.88,0:04:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們小倆口去院子聊天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.18,0:04:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去啊去啊,明日菜小姐也去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.26,0:04:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先要讓雙方的父母見個面才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.06,0:04:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,沒錯沒錯,的確該見個面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.49,0:05:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經秋天了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.76,0:05:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.33,0:05:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我跟妳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.63,0:05:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.34,0:05:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.34,0:05:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡秋天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.15,0:05:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜歡秋天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.98,0:05:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有春天、夏天、冬天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.46,0:05:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果也能像這樣\N和你一起渡過不知道有多好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.66,0:06:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以在這時候退縮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.00,0:06:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟妳說一件\N不是什麼愉快的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.81,0:06:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳冷靜聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.88,0:06:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的,我無法和妳結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.79,0:06:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該早跟妳說清楚才對…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.72,0:06:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道該怎麼向妳道歉才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.22,0:06:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.07,0:06:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振…振作一點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.25,0:07:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像妳這麼美麗的人\N一定可以遇到更好的對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.60,0:07:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要出家當尼姑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.43,0:07:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一輩子不結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.40,0:07:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.61,0:07:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是討厭我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.85,0:07:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會討厭妳呢\N不是這個原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.79,0:07:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來你不討厭我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.86,0:07:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然不討厭,只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.73,0:07:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.43,0:07:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有你這句話,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.77,0:07:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳能諒解我的心情了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.34,0:07:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師,我去上學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.97,0:08:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.74,0:08:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師,今天晚餐\N你想吃什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.38,0:08:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說妳啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.45,0:08:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壽喜燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.22,0:08:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊,哦,沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.82,0:08:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我會早點回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.39,0:08:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛肉要買霜降肉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.13,0:08:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儼然一副老婆的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.66,0:08:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會在那邊看笑話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.60,0:08:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一大早你在做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.87,0:08:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在做積木,積木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.70,0:08:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,積木?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.84,0:09:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著要上色,然後畫圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.64,0:09:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.41,0:09:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.75,0:09:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.85,0:09:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他今天好開朗喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.02,0:09:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像發生了什麼好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.95,0:09:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起喔\N今天沒有時間陪你玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.89,0:09:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.00,0:09:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐,告訴妳一個好消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.66,0:09:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.13,0:09:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳等了這麼久\N我終於拒絕相親的婚事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.34,0:09:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我是自由之身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.31,0:09:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們之間的障礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.01,0:09:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經完全消除了,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.65,0:09:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.95,0:09:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼啊,一大早就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.78,0:09:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.02,0:09:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我跟音無小姐的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.29,0:09:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜\N那是樁不錯的婚事不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.69,0:09:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是貫徹我的真心\N絕沒有後悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.80,0:10:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個星期六妳有空嗎?\N我們一起去吃個飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.40,0:10:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉,星期六我有事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.27,0:10:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去給我先生掃墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.85,0:10:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔,秋分掃墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.58,0:10:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉\N我實在太欠缺考慮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡,別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.02,0:10:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳先生喜歡吃什麼?\N喜歡什麼花?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算要一起去掃墓嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.53,0:10:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,我只是隨口問問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.20,0:10:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他那個人不太挑剔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花應該是喜歡菊花…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.44,0:10:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菊花?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.10,0:10:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,而且可以拿來做醬菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.67,0:10:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菊花啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.37,0:10:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,音無小姐\N今天我就此告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.61,0:10:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才剛來就要走了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.55,0:10:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經告訴了妳\N我是為了妳拒絕相親的婚事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.08,0:10:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說,今天看來我也無法\N進入妳的心裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.13,0:11:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好老套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.06,0:11:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下妳打算怎麼辦?管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.10,0:11:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看他會故意跑去掃墓\N然後在妳爸媽面前向妳求婚喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.01,0:11:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.61,0:11:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.72,0:11:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員\N洗衣機借我用一下好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.29,0:11:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.32,0:11:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹也蠻敢的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.13,0:11:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人最怕攻勢強烈的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.07,0:11:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你也最好處理一下\N身邊女人的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.64,0:11:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒那些問題\N你跟他也差太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.63,0:12:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,麻煩妳看家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.30,0:12:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,妳就放輕鬆點去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.10,0:12:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我向妳爸媽問好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.77,0:12:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.69,0:12:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了,去工作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員她老公的墳墓在哪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.47,0:12:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得好像是在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.34,0:12:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是他?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.87,0:12:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大嬸,這是誰打來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你猜猜看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.08,0:12:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.61,0:12:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猜對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.85,0:13:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他問管理員老公的墳墓在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.02,0:13:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜他可能想在管理員爸媽面前\N向管理員求婚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個不要臉的男人\N一定會這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.26,0:13:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.59,0:13:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.96,0:13:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.40,0:13:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你來這裡做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.40,0:13:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才是呢\N你到底在打什麼主意?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.01,0:14:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是來向她老公打個招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.68,0:14:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴他\N我一定會讓音無小姐幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.18,0:14:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也很欣慰的答應了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.12,0:14:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起謊來\N竟然臉不紅氣不喘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.56,0:14:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也已經上完香了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.09,0:14:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓開,我要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.59,0:14:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拖到這麼晚真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.36,0:14:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點離開這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.00,0:14:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.63,0:14:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老公搞錯會合的時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.64,0:14:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是妳搞錯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.90,0:14:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.81,0:14:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也經常因為這樣\N被我老婆罵呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.87,0:14:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,是她,是她搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.44,0:14:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,是誰來過了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.71,0:14:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像才剛走的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.32,0:14:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這束花看起來很貴喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.29,0:14:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.96,0:14:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是五代的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.73,0:14:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.13,0:15:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能繼續躲在這裡\N不然還能怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.61,0:15:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代來這裡做什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.68,0:15:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,這束花也是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.95,0:15:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.36,0:15:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,是卡片嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.76,0:15:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.36,0:15:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹不就是那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.06,0:15:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,他是妳的朋友嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.30,0:15:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,響子跟他正在交往…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.97,0:15:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.80,0:15:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的網球教練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.84,0:15:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.68,0:15:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只是這樣吧\N這孩子害羞不好意思說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.18,0:15:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.18,0:15:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係,沒有必要隱瞞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.02,0:15:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我隱瞞什麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.33,0:16:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.79,0:16:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子終於想要再婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.30,0:16:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.33,0:16:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.97,0:16:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來我也安心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.84,0:16:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直把妳綁在音無家\N對妳也說不過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.05,0:16:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,不是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.85,0:16:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事當然也要跟\N惣一郎報告才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.12,0:16:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,你聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.62,0:16:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定也會很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.59,0:16:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對啊,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.56,0:16:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.60,0:16:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想再婚了,對不對?響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.98,0:16:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.05,0:16:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.02,0:17:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.02,0:17:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有想要再婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.19,0:17:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.69,0:17:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.20,0:17:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會在這裡遇見妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.97,0:17:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,三鷹先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.87,0:17:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙,什麼時候跑出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.51,0:17:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,你還沒走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.81,0:17:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來想馬上就回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.85,0:17:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是想多了解一下\N她先生長眠的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.55,0:17:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在鬼扯什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.29,0:17:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹先生,這位是響子的公公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.06,0:17:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,她先生的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.96,0:17:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.76,0:17:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡,不好意思,隨便來上香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.66,0:17:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也別在那裡發愣\N快點過來打個招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.00,0:17:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.20,0:17:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點過來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.17,0:17:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.11,0:17:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.68,0:18:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長得一表人才蠻不錯的嘛,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.72,0:18:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個真的很登對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.05,0:18:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛,而且家世還好到\N響子幾乎高攀不上呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.99,0:18:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡,沒有啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.89,0:18:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.53,0:18:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站在這裡講話也不是辦法\N去找個地方坐下來喝茶慢慢聊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.90,0:18:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.93,0:18:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.37,0:18:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,妳在做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.21,0:18:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想再祭拜一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.98,0:18:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊\N那我們在前面的咖啡店等妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.43,0:18:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.73,0:18:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉\N這並不是我的原意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.56,0:18:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想來向妳先生打個招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.94,0:19:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳一定不相信吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.87,0:19:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會啊,我怎麼會不相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.21,0:19:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.21,0:19:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.15,0:19:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳一定要相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.15,0:19:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不是有意來打擾妳掃墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.22,0:19:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.62,0:19:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼扯大王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.65,0:19:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.16,0:19:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再婚的話\N你真的能安心嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.80,0:20:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定反而會讓你更擔心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.97,0:20:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個人真的很靠不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.42,0:20:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.92,0:20:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了春天,他一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.25,0:20:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不過,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.75,0:20:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說再婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.69,0:21:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不是現在馬上就要結婚喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.49,0:21:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你不用去幼稚園嗎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.57,0:21:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們都在等你耶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.14,0:21:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.11,0:21:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.35,0:21:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在春天來臨之前\N我都會是一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.04,0:21:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.74,0:21:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.77,0:21:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會找到工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.01,0:21:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為獨當一面的男子漢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.01,0:21:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以到了春天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.45,0:21:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了春天我一定會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.55,0:21:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.59,0:22:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.06,0:22:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼慢才來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.56,0:22:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,有點事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.96,0:22:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.60,0:22:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請給我一杯咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.83,0:22:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.74,0:22:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,口好渴喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.48,0:22:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.88,0:22:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我們聊了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.95,0:22:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說三鷹先生為了妳\N還拒絕了一樁好婚事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.69,0:22:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望妳不要誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.46,0:22:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並非我拒絕了相親的婚事\N就要妳嫁給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.40,0:22:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣單方面的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.00,0:22:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我而言,音無小姐是\N值得拋棄一切在所不惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.04,0:22:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一讓我想廝守終生的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.34,0:22:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了不起的覺悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.57,0:22:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子真的好幸福喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.35,0:23:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟明日菜的相親\N讓我領悟到一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.52,0:23:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是終身大事可以完全無視\N當事者的意願而進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.22,0:23:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家長的力量真的很恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.66,0:23:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父親雖然看起來很頑固
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.32,0:23:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不論用什麼手段一定要說服他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.70,0:23:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要讓他答應我們的婚事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.60,0:23:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.94,0:23:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃,沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.12,0:23:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,五代,收下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.56,0:23:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下子工作敲定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.76,0:23:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要,我拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.86,0:23:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.90,0:23:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,妳快回家去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.07,0:23:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.64,0:23:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,『五代幹得好!\N偶爾展現男子氣概』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.01,0:24:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他在想什麼,居然還耍酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.62,0:24:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人坐在黎明的護欄上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.20,0:24:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今一直在尋找遺落愛的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.89,0:24:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.09,0:24:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…一陣風…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.53,0:25:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目光交會…只有…再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.47,0:25:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.64,0:25:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…在雨中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.08,0:25:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忽然…胸口…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.41,0:25:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢…濡濕而發光
